# Broadcasting Tests (Future Multi-AI)

Test broadcasting messages to multiple AI backends.
Note: Currently only works with ollama, but demonstrates the API for future multi-AI support.

## Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@sessionId = REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID

### Broadcast to All Backends in Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello from broadcast! Each AI should respond with their name."
}

### Broadcast to Specific Backends
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "What's the square root of 16?",
  "backends": ["ollama"]
}

### Get All Responses After Broadcast
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/{{sessionId}}/messages

### Create Multi-Backend Session for Testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backends": ["ollama"],
  "name": "Broadcast Test Session",
  "metadata": {
    "purpose": "testing_broadcast_functionality"
  }
}
